{
  "id": "adv_card_ski_03_02",
  "title": "白石沙季 2話 自分自身を貫く",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-evening",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "― The next day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、こんにちは\n……これ、見てもらえないでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ hello.\n…Could you take a look at this?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "これは……有名なロックミュージシャンの本と\nドキュメンタリーのDVDか。借りてきたのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is… a book by a famous rock musician\nand a documentary DVD. Did you borrow them?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "はい、明日はオフなので\n部屋でじっくり勉強するつもりです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ since tomorrow is my day off‚\nI plan to study them carefully in my room",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "少しでもステージで弾けるためのヒントに\nなればいいなって思って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hoping to find some hints\nto be more vibrant on stage…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "いつになく本気だな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You seem unusually serious…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "期待していて下さいね\nこれまでとは違う私を、お見せしますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please look forward to it.\nI'll show you a different side of me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（気合いが入り過ぎている気がするぞ……不安だ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(She seems to be putting too much effort… I'm worried.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――そして、翌日の夜",
      "translations": {
        "en": "―And the next night",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_corridor_night",
      "startTime": 41.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ……へっへ\n私にはあんなのは、ぜえったい無理……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fu fu… heh heh.\nThat's absolutely impossible for me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.7409753443,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "沙季！　どうしたんだ？\nふらふらして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Saki! What's wrong?\nYou look dizzy…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "はっ！？\n……{user}さん、お疲れ様です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh!?\n…{user}-san‚ hi.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "その……部屋で\nロックミュージシャンのDVDを観ていたのですが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um… I was watching a DVD of\na rock musician in my room‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "音楽は、それはもう素晴らしかったです\n強烈な音に、体が揺さぶられるようで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The music was absolutely fantastic.\nIt shook my body with its intense sound…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "ステージパフォーマンスも本当に格好良くて\n私も観に行ってみたいと思うくらいでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The stage performance was really cool too‚\nIt made me want to go and see it myself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そうか、参考になったようだな。良かったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see‚ seems like it was helpful. That's good.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02-ski011.m4a",
      "text": "ですが……ステージで流血沙汰を起こして\nしかも歌手がお客さんを殴るとはどういうことですか！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "However… causing bloody fights on stage‚\nAnd the singer punching the audience‚ what's that about?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02-ski012.m4a",
      "text": "服はいつもだらしなくて\nジーンズなんてお尻にまで穴が空いてるし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The clothes are always sloppy‚\nThe jeans even have holes all the way to the butt…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02-ski013.m4a",
      "text": "貯金もしないで、一晩で大金を使い果たして！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Spending a fortune in one night without saving anything!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02-ski014.m4a",
      "text": "暴飲暴食を繰り返して、ライブの直前だけ\n過激なダイエット、あれでは体を壊して当然です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Repeating episodes of excessive eating and drinking‚ and right before the live‚\nEngaging in extreme diets‚ it's only natural to ruin one's health!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（……一体、どんなミュージシャンを勉強したんだ？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(…What kind of musician did she study?)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02-ski015.m4a",
      "text": "それに……それにですよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And… and also…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02-ski016.m4a",
      "text": "公衆の面前で、恋人とあんなにいちゃいちゃ……\n人目もはばからずに、あんなにべたべた……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Publicly‚ being so lovey-dovey with their lover…\nNot caring about others watching‚ being all touchy-feely…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02-ski017.m4a",
      "text": "もう……観ているだけで恥ずかしかった……です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was so… embarrassing just to watch…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（……沙季には、少し）\n（刺激が強かったのかもしれないな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(…Perhaps Saki was affected a bit)\n(by something too stimulating.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02-ski018.m4a",
      "text": "こ……こほん\n失礼しました、なんだか変なことまで言ってしまって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ko… kohon.\nI apologize‚ I ended up saying weird things.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02-ski019.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん相手だと\nついつい話し過ぎてしまって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's because it's you‚ {user}-san‚\nI unintentionally talk too much…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02-ski020.m4a",
      "text": "すみません。これは気のゆるみですね\nでも他の子に、こんな恥ずかしいこと言えませんから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry. It's just a slip of the tongue.\nBut I can't say such embarrassing things to the others.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "いや、みんなには話し辛い相談があれば\n遠慮なく俺に言ってくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ if you have any difficult discussions that you can't\ntalk to others about‚ feel free to talk to me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.2780958055,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02-ski021.m4a",
      "text": "はい、頼りにしていますね\n{user}さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ok‚ I'll rely on you.\n{user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.0501137297,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02-ski022.m4a",
      "text": "それで……公衆の面前でいちゃいちゃ……はともかく\n調べてみて、分かったこともあった、と思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So… aside from being lovey-dovey in public…\nI looked into it and I think I understood something.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 173.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "どんなことだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What is it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 177.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
