      "text": "立ち居振る舞いは、酷い、の一語でしたけど\nそれでも――彼らは、偉大で、弾けていました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Their behavior was described as terrible‚\nbut even so‚ they were great and vibrant.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 182.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02-ski024.m4a",
      "text": "弾けて見えるのは\n優れた技術や破天荒なあれこれだけじゃなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The vibrancy doesn't come just from\nexceptional skills or unconventional things…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 188.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02-ski025.m4a",
      "text": "何か他に大きな理由があったから、そんな気がします\nでも、それがなんなのかまでは分からなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I feel like there must be another significant reason behind it‚\nbut I don't know what it is…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 198.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな……彼らは自分自身を貫いたから\n結果、そう見えた……とか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… They stayed true to themselves‚\nand as a result‚ it appeared that way… or something like that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 208.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02-ski026.m4a",
      "text": "自分を貫いて……\nそれを、ステージの上で表現する？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Staying true to themselves…\nExpressing that on the stage?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 214.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_02-ski027.m4a",
      "text": "……そんなこと、私に……出来るのでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Can I really do something like that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 218.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
