      "text": "沙季になら、きっと出来るよ\nいや、沙季だからこそ出来る……俺はそう思ってる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sure you can‚ Saki.\nNo‚ precisely because it's you‚ Saki… that's what I believe.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 226.4,
